## SCA — Security Configuration Assessment
Checks your device against CIS Benchmark security standards.

| Score | Status |
|---|---|
| Above 80% | Good ✅ |
| 60-80% | Needs improvement ⚠️ |
| Below 60% | High risk — fix immediately 🔴 |

Common SCA failures:
- Default administrator account not renamed
- Guest account not disabled
- Unencrypted traffic allowed
- Basic authentication enabled
- Audit logging not configured

